0MQ Binding for Delphi
======================

The aim of thw project is to bring 0MQ to the Delphi comunity. 

General
=======

The package contains a wrapper (zmq.pas) for the dll, a delphi translation 
for the C++ Api (zmqcpp.pas), and a higher level api (zmqapi.pas). 

Examples
========

in the examples directory there are some examples translated from the guide.

